reviews.text: Staff is very friendly. Food is delicious! Definitely try their smoothies. I would recommend the strawberry cheesecake and the energy booster

Hard to say... The staff were nice but they were all sleeping behind the wheel.  Example... They bring you your food and would walk away when there are no knives and forks... In another incident, you ask for a pitcher and they return to ask if it's a glass or pitcher we ordered... It was a rather frustrating experience for food that were so ordinary

I had the omelet on Sunday morning after a swim and it was very good. Be service was okay except they forgot my wife’s lemonade. It’s got a very nice view of the beach and the people are friendly. Great brunch spot.
Great atmosphere but unfortunately, food and service disappoints. The server seems nonchalant and aren't proactive in serving customers. What a shame....

Nice cafe just off the beach, with big patio doors that open on to the beach promenade.

They are good for coffee and breakfast/brunch food. The breakfasts seem to have improved recently. The Full English now has thick it bacon (2 slices) and a big thick sausage. Other dishes like Mac & Cheese are good. 
This place is always a reliable venue for food and coffee once you step off the beach.

reviews.text: It was a great place! Good location next to repulse bay with restaurants of different cuisines. I enjoyed the beer festival very much, good spots for photo taking and the food and and beer were stunning! Perfect for weekend activities.
Nice location in the rooftop. Good unique beers to try out, great view with the bay and very special ladder for photos. Wish it's bigger and more stalls.

Went to the Pirate's Beer Fest today and had a total blast.  There's a great selection of food and beer available, staff are uber friendly and helpful.  The game stalls were fun as well, won myself a frog and banana plushie.  There are cabanas on one side of the venue and great photo taking spots. Overall was a good day out!
Nice place. Terrace on the beach with premium beers. Highly recommendable
Nice beach with many amenities and a grocery store all within an area.
